Package com.stormpath.sdk.saml

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AssertionConsumerServicePostEndpoint
    The Stormpath endpoint that will process SAML Assertions sent by the SAML Identity Provider for a specific Stormpath Directory.
    AttributeStatementMappingRule
    A rule that indicates how a SAML Attribute Statement should populate one or more Stormpath Account field values.
    AttributeStatementMappingRuleBuilder
    A Builder to construct AttributeStatementMappingRule resources.
    AttributeStatementMappingRules
    An ordered Set of all AttributeStatementMappingRules that indicate how SAML Attribute Statements should populate one or more Stormpath Account field values after a successful SAML login.
    AttributeStatementMappingRulesBuilder
    A Builder to construct AttributeStatementMappingRules resources.
    AuthnVerification
    An AuthnVerification represents the successful results of verifying the signature of a SAML AuthnRequest targeted against a particular Stormpath Application.
    AuthnVerificationRequest
    An AuthnVerificationRequest encapsulates the fields of a SAML AuthnRequest targeted against a particular Stormpath Application.
    CreateRegisteredSamlServiceProviderRequest
    Represents an attempt to create a new RegisteredSamlServiceProvider record in Stormpath.
    CreateRegisteredSamlServiceProviderRequestBuilder
    A Builder to construct CreateRegisteredSamlServiceProviderRequests.
    CreateSamlResponseRequest
    A SamlResponseRequest encapsulates the information needed to prepare a SAML response according to the SAML specification.
    CreateSamlServiceProviderRegistrationRequest
    Represents an attempt to create a new SamlServiceProviderRegistration record in Stormpath.
    CreateSamlServiceProviderRegistrationRequestBuilder
    A Builder to construct CreateSamlServiceProviderRegistrationRequests.
    RegisteredSamlServiceProvider
    A registeredSamlServiceProvider is associated with an Tenant and represents a service provider for Stormpath as an identity provider flow.
    RegisteredSamlServiceProviderCriteria
    A RegisteredSamlServiceProvider-specific Criteria class, enabling a RegisteredSamlServiceProvider-specific fluentquery DSL.
    RegisteredSamlServiceProviderList
    A CollectionResource containing RegisteredSamlServiceProvider instances.
    RegisteredSamlServiceProviderOptions<T>
    RegisteredSamlServiceProvider-specific options that may be specified when retrieving RegisteredSamlServiceProvider resources.
    SamlCallbackHandler
    Handles HTTP replies sent from your SAML Identity Provider to your application's callbackUri, for example, https://awesomeapp.com/userHome, and returns an AccountResult.
    SamlIdentityProvider
    A SamlIdentityProvider represents data supporting Stormpath as an saml identity provider.
    SamlIdentityProviderCriteria
    A SamlIdentityProvider-specific Criteria class, enabling a SamlIdentityProvider-specific fluentquery DSL.
    SamlIdentityProviderMetadata
    The (read-only) Saml Identity Provider metadata providing meta data for a given Stormpath's Application as part of its SamlPolicy
    SamlIdentityProviderOptions<T>
    SamlIdentityProvider-specific options that may be specified when retrieving SamlIdentityProvider resources.
    SamlIdpUrlBuilder
    A Builder design pattern used to construct a URL you can use to redirect application users to a SAML authentication site (Identity Provider or IdP) for performing common user identity functionality.
    SamlPolicy
    A SamlPolicy represents an Application's SAML-specific configuration.
    SamlResponse
    A SamlResponse has a single field whose value is the base 64 encoded XML of a SAML response according to the SAML specification.
    SamlResultListener
    Listener interface to get notifications about effective operations of the SAML IdP invocation: authentication or logout.
    SamlServiceProvider
    A SamlServiceProvider instance represents the information necessary to redirect an end-user to login at a SAML Identity Provider.
    SamlServiceProviderMetadata
    The (read-only) Service Provider metadata that can be used to register an application (aka 'Service Provider) with a SAML Identity Provider.
    SamlServiceProviderRegistration
    A SamlServiceProviderRegistration represents the link between a SamlIdentityProvider and a RegisteredSamlServiceProvider
    SamlServiceProviderRegistrationCriteria
    A SamlServiceProviderRegistration-specific Criteria class, enabling a SamlServiceProviderRegistration-specific fluentquery DSL.
    SamlServiceProviderRegistrationList
    A CollectionResource containing SamlServiceProviderRegistration instances.
    SamlServiceProviderRegistrationOptions<T>
    SamlServiceProviderRegistration-specific options that may be specified when retrieving SamlServiceProviderRegistration resources.
    SsoInitiationEndpoint
